Package: spade
Title: Spade Block Authoring Library for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Spade", "Developers", email = "dev@spade.dev",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Runtime library for authoring Spade blocks in R. Provides S4
    types for file and directory inputs/outputs, a run() function that handles
    parameter loading, input scanning, handler invocation, and output writing,
    and a build() function for generating block manifests from function signatures.
